    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>★ 此版本为体验版 ★</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >－体验版可游玩至游戏中的第 5 天早上，约 1 ~ 2 小时的游戏时长</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >－可遇到两名可追求的好感角色，进行对话、送礼、探险邀请</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >P.S. 若要将体验版的存档移至正式版继续使用，可参考讨论区的置顶教学！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras/2ca263752d6ccd73f8bc60a773137f34.webp?t=1765351503\" width=600 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款结合战斗与生活模拟的限时类轻养成游戏，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将扮演实习中的炼金术士，为了向父母证明自己的能力，独自前往亚斯达小镇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这 90 天内，你可以自由安排时间，去小镇上课、打工，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或是邀约伙伴，去镇外的探险地收集素材，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着时间的推移，你也可以前往附近的群岛，或是参与小镇内的节日活动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总之，这 90 天，就是属于你的日子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras/2ef2c23231b69977d5220100b5165fec.webp?t=1765351503\" width=600 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆  炼制药剂：为了赚取更多金钱和交货点数，认真炼制药剂吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras/611080e65591c8827acf1fc4e4725b86.avif?t=1765351503\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆  战斗系统：加入【天气操控】及【状态平衡值 BP】，拥有更丰富的战斗策略！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras/0545ec53cf013edef9f00669e8871d55.poster.avif?t=1765351503\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras/0545ec53cf013edef9f00669e8871d55.webm?t=1765351503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras/0545ec53cf013edef9f00669e8871d55.mp4?t=1765351503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ 骑鸡泡澡：体力不够的时候，就跟鸡仔一起泡澡来恢复体力吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras/26cfafa03792e5c78b22d12186184970.poster.avif?t=1765351503\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras/26cfafa03792e5c78b22d12186184970.webm?t=1765351503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras/26cfafa03792e5c78b22d12186184970.mp4?t=1765351503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆  好感角色：想更进一步了解他们吗？可以透过对话、送礼，以及邀请探险来有更多互动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras/f13056df4c2808dbab914372fb198eff.avif?t=1765351503\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124410/extras_big/f13056df4c2808dbab914372fb198eff.avif?t=1765351503 width=800 height=271 /></span></p>",
